metadata.name: Crypto World
metadata.description: Welcome to Crypto World! This is my own idea of how I see the world of Cryptocurrencies. Right after the birth of Bitcoin back in 2009, other cryptocurrencies were born such as ETH , BAT, and LTC and much more. The world has seen the evolution of Cryptocurrencies and the impact that Bitcoin has had in so many ways such as bringing more freedom to people. There will only be 100 copies of these art-work but as of now there's only 25 available. Get yours before it's too late!
